The client always acknowledges each request it gets.
The application will wait on this acknowledgement before proceeding.

Communication thread:
    pops commands from the queue
    sends commands to the drone and receives responses.

Gesture thread:
    detects gestures from the Leap motion by polling the controller.
    On detected gesture, it sends commands by pushing them onto a queue.


